c: 11
v: 14
t: "Tokkel Nabii Mucammadow cgale koo kee kô luk yeemene mari ama koros isin fan ken kak sectaanam siinik cineenik, toysa moominiiney isin ama Qhuraan cagalah Yalli caglitah yan ixxigal isi farmoytal obiseh yan kitab kinnim ixiga, isin cakkil yaqbuden Yalli anee waam ixiga inki Yallak sa, tokkel isin Yallaa kee kay farmoytih amri oggolteenii"